Fetching 'awesome_customers_windows' from source at .
Fetching cookbook index from https://supermarket.chef.io...
Using awesome_customers_windows (0.1.0) from source at .
```

Now run `kitchen converge`. This command brings up a Windows Server instance, installs `chef-client`, and applies the cookbook.

```bash
